{"tid":40093,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"200GB左右SSD求推薦","createTime":"2016-12-15T03:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T15:11:59.000Z","uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbb42bbf1f8ae8e62a18b27ccbc5e8ccd20587c","tid":40093,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"想買隻200GB左右的SSD裝os同幾隻game (主要係overwatch 同 lol）<br />\n<br />\n想請問邊隻最抵屌 最緊要襟用<br />\n<br />\n上一隻用左1年左右就打柴 仲要嗰陣淨係裝os<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知係咪成日掃毒搞到咁快壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望各位連登仔賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n筆直500"},{"pid":"c09075c5d07b65d4d6d1ba975198d70e36ac634f","tid":40093,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"kingston uv400 240gb"},{"pid":"66d7b390a33f6bd65aa420fd9e302b9ea3bcdf1b","tid":40093,"uid":61259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"Plextor M7V 256GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d29a4dae7def1a4a80e4899f88e344d6e759c5","tid":40093,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"apdator sp550"},{"pid":"5c597f211be220def719554eb1ca636608aecebf","tid":40093,"uid":31545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌"},{"pid":"059860effe8dc2a646c2932fff7e748450d9e672","tid":40093,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨system 就百二算啦"},{"pid":"9a30fba004f59e303dde22443121f28934d59743","tid":40093,"uid":11952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"除Adat之外其他都可以，只Adat每3個月死一次，嬲撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82927a18664d45bff848983ad41e73f512ace339","tid":40093,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kingston uv400 240gb</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該悠二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061289fd59813c26bf15b89a9718ac48fd01c750","tid":40093,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Plextor M7V 256GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次就係買呢個牌子的SSD 120GB（好似係120）<br />\n<br />\n用咗大半年就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e5a46b65e35608ccfb2fa7ef30319f7493fca","tid":40093,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除Adat之外其他都可以，只Adat每3個月死一次，嬲撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死SSD真係嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用HDD又頂唔順佢咁慢<br />\n<br />\n巴打仲要每3個月死1次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45badad2632611b4c37ae0b4620628d7cf444739","tid":40093,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裝喺SSD loading點都快過HDD<br />\n<br />\n譬如玩LOL，揀完角色大家一齊load入去個場度果陣就會好清晰咁睇到你用SSD同人地用HDD嘅分別。"},{"pid":"c32e13606da159e442986e50c6aae72cbfe8979e","tid":40093,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裝喺SSD loading點都快過HDD<br />\n<br />\n譬如玩LOL，揀完角色大家一齊load入去個場度果陣就會好清晰咁睇到你用SSD同人地用HDD嘅分別。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題你係要等埋其他人load 完先入得去。<br />\n<br />\n10個人有9個SSD, 一個人HDD, 都係慢"},{"pid":"415b00510d632d22d996a67d2e3cbae03370bf4b","tid":40093,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裝喺SSD loading點都快過HDD<br />\n<br />\n譬如玩LOL，揀完角色大家一齊load入去個場度果陣就會好清晰咁睇到你用SSD同人地用HDD嘅分別。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題你係要等埋其他人load 完先入得去。<br />\n<br />\n10個人有9個SSD, 一個人HDD, 都係慢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至少到時你唔會係拖慢成村人果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09ca17327605297576ef4b6e8d8808a937f6461","tid":40093,"uid":18877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"玩Path of Exile你就會好清楚SSD同HDD既分別"},{"pid":"7ead55e5f41fe91743332fc493f5e2fb09158901","tid":40093,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我嘅理解係連線game係唔使裝係ssd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錯勿屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n裝喺SSD loading點都快過HDD<br />\n<br />\n譬如玩LOL，揀完角色大家一齊load入去個場度果陣就會好清晰咁睇到你用SSD同人地用HDD嘅分別。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題你係要等埋其他人load 完先入得去。<br />\n<br />\n10個人有9個SSD, 一個人HDD, 都係慢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至少到時你唔會係拖慢成村人果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁實有快有慢架啦 累街坊都要睇係邊種 有d load差唔多1分鐘真係屌老母<br />\n不過上面講緊個重點都係load入場要等其他人 自己好撚快都係用黎打飛機咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed3d4388dc87876c176203c84050660ee1dbfb9","tid":40093,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"騎劫下for文書file用 有無介紹 最緊要認到舊機(win97,2000)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca82fc450a4adfda3dce290f4c7c5491978a6168","tid":40093,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"台灣佬評價<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FStorage_Zone%2FM.1447390455.A.34C.html&d=hYX%2BYVn9IVBUCSgwV1kXpmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=cb49db69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己就用WD既"},{"pid":"9bb8dd3fd0208930c78794ce48f417dcf0c0d040","tid":40093,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣佬評價<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FStorage_Zone%2FM.1447390455.A.34C.html&d=hYX%2BYVn9IVBUCSgwV1kXpmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=cb49db69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己就用WD既</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FStorage_Zone%2FM.1447390455.A.34C.html%20&d=hYX%2BYVn9IVBUCSgwV1kXpmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=45f9eda4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Storage_Zone/M.1447390455.A.34C.html </a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb9897325dcffb6fbb2bf0a7cf780d9acc02669","tid":40093,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:27: